t#Latin\" title=\"amat\">amat</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/bene#Latin\" title=\"bene\">bene</a> <a href=\"/wiki/castigat#Latin\" title=\"castigat\">cast&#x12B;gat</a></strong>\n</p><ol><li><a href=\"/wiki/spare_the_rod_and_spoil_the_child\" title=\"spare the rod and spoil the child\">spare the rod and spoil the child</a></li></ol></div>"
